==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Herbage
<hw>Herb"age</hw> <pr>(?; 48)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. See
<er>Herb</er>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Herbs collectively; green food beasts; grass;
pasture.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧Thin <xex>herbage</xex> in the plaims.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Law.)</fld> <def>The liberty or right of pasture in
the forest or in the grounds of another man.</def>
<rj><au>Blount.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Herbaged</ent>⟦br⟧
